Project copy of global `sdk-flutter-stack.mdc`. See also `language-dart-flutter.mdc` and `code-standards.mdc`.

## Codegen (this repo)

```bash
scripts/codegen.sh    # slang + build_runner for whole repo
```

Never hand-edit `*.g.dart`, `*.freezed.dart`, `strings*.g.dart`.

## Stack routing

| Package | Role |
|---------|------|
| **provider** | App-wide `ChangeNotifier` state ‚Äî register in `main.dart` |
| **drift** | `AppDatabase` ‚Äî bump `schemaVersion` + migration |
| **slang** | `lib/i18n/*.i18n.json` ‚Üí `t.*` |
| **freezed** + **json_serializable** | Models in `lib/` and `packages/emby_core/` |
| **dio** | HTTP in emby_core only ‚Äî app uses `EmbyClient` |

## State management

- One canonical provider per domain; coalesce concurrent loads.
- `context.read<T>()` in callbacks; `context.watch<T>()` when UI rebuilds.
- Dispose listeners in `DisposableChangeNotifierMixin`.

## Persistence

- Drift for structured data; SharedPreferences via `SettingsService` / `BaseSharedPreferencesService`.
- Never store raw tokens in logs ‚Äî use `AppLogger`.

## Forbidden

- GetX / Riverpod unless project adopts them
- Manual JSON when freezed is standard
- Hardcoded user strings (use slang)
